## Cdetheme 1.4.2 - December 2022 (Updated for Python 3 and GTK 4.x)

Cde front panel and gtk/qt/xfce theme. Mainly meant to use with
xfce4.  Logged in to an xfce session, run 

./startpanel

to install the theme  on first run and start the front panel. 

The cdepanel and gtk/qt themes have been updated to use Python 3
and include GTK 4.x support. The project now includes:
- Python 3.x compatibility
- GTK 2.0, 3.16, 3.20, and 4.x theme support
- Updated PyInstaller configuration for Python 3

Please do not use 'minimal xfce install', that won't work.

